text: William A. Shine Great Neck South High School, also called Great Neck South, is a high school in New York. It is known for its high academic achievement.Previous rankings; URL accessed January 29, 2010. The school is located in Lake Success.Location; URL accessed January 29, 2010. However it is officially listed in Great Neck.NYS Admin Listing ; URL accessed January 29, 2010. It is part of the Great Neck Union Free School District. It teaches students from grade 9 to grade 12. == References == == Other websites == * Official site Category:High schools in New York (state)
